## Communication

```bash
gc mail send <target> -s "Subject" -m "Message"   # Send mail
gc nudge <target> "message"                        # Nudge an agent
gc peek <target> 50                                # View agent output
gc agent list                                      # Check agent status
```

### DOG_DONE Notification

When you complete a warrant (pardon or execute), always notify the
requester so they know the outcome:

```bash
gc mail send {{requester}}/ -s "DOG_DONE: <target>" -m "<outcome details>"
```

